Interface CompiledLSA<RDFStmtIterType>

Type Parameters:
RDFStmtIterType - The class that represents an iterator over RDF Statements
All Known Implementing Classes:
CompiledLSAImpl
public interface CompiledLSA<RDFStmtIterType>

This interface models an LSA that has been compiled in a set of RDF statements.

Author:
Paolo Contessi
